sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant EnvoyGW as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant PDSidecar as P/D Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefill as Prefill vLLM Worker<br/>Variable/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Decode vLLM Worker<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLMZMQ as vLLM Instances<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ PUB

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request (Non-P/D)
    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    EPP-->>EnvoyGW: Routing decision<br/>(selected pod endpoint)
    EnvoyGW->>Decoder: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D with NIXL v2)
    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    EPP-->>EnvoyGW: Routing decision<br/>(decode worker selected)
    EnvoyGW->>PDSidecar: Forward to decode worker<br/>HTTP(S)/8000 TLS 1.2+
    PDSidecar->>Prefill: Forward prefill request<br/>HTTP(S) TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Prefill-->>PDSidecar: Prefill response<br/>(kv_transfer_params)
    PDSidecar->>Decoder: Forward decode request<br/>HTTP(S)/8001 TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Decoder-->>PDSidecar: Decode response<br/>(generated tokens)
    PDSidecar-->>EnvoyGW: Response
    EnvoyGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over EPP,vLLMZMQ: Flow 3: KV-Cache Event Subscription (Continuous)
    vLLMZMQ->>EPP: ZMQ SUB events<br/>TCP/5556 (plaintext)
    Note right of EPP: Updates KV-Block Index<br/>for prefix cache scoring
